data.title: Sanaya Irani, Jennifer Winget, Hina Khan, Shivangi Joshi, Nia Sharma Are ASIA'S SEXIEST Women
data.meta_description: Priyanka Chopra and Deepika Padukone are on this list, and so are 16 smoking hot Indian women, all from the world of small screen. Sanaya Irani, Hina Khan, Jennifer Winget, Nia Sharma, Anita Hassanandani, Drashti Dhami sit pretty on this illustrious listing... | Read at SpotboyE
data.text:
Eastern Eye 50 Sexiest Asian Women List 2017 is out and some of Indian television’s hottest ladies are on it. In fact, 16 out of the 50 spots, have been claimed by Indian TV's leading lights. It’s interesting that small screen actress Nia Sharma is next only to international star Priyanka Chopra, who tops this year's list.

Nia is on number 2 position, a notch up from last year’s 3rd spot. And following her are these sensational beauties who have made it to the list.

The breathtaking Drashti Dhami known for her role in Dill Mill Gayye (Star One) is a new entrant on the list.

Hugely popular on the small screen and much in news for stirring up a storm on Bigg Boss 11, on the list is the HOT HOT Hina Khan.

Model-turned-actress Sanaya Irani best known for Iss Pyaar Ko Kya Naam Doon (Star Plus), turns up the heat on the popular listing.

Also on the list is former Bigg Boss contestant Gauhar Khan.

A loud shout for the lead star of the show Choti Bahu - Sinduur Bin Suhagan (Zee TV), Rubina Dilaik.

Small screen's beloved girl, Anita Hassanandani, features on the list.

The very talented and the scorching hot Beyhadh (Sony TV) star Jennifer Winget,is also one of the sexiest women In Asia.

TV actress Surbhi Chandana, who played the parallel lead in Zee TV’s popular daily soap Qubool Hai, also has the honour of being on the list.

And, how could the list not feature the smoking hot Shivangi Joshi...

Extremely popular on the small screen and social media, TV hottie Helly Shah, is also on the list.

Meet the gorgeous Shivani Tomar, who’s beauty is heartbreaking to say the least

Harshita Gaur of Sadda Haq (Channel V) makes her debut on the list.

23-year-old Niti Taylor rubs shoulders with other TV hotties...

Make way for Tejaswi Prakash, best known for playing the role of Ragini Lakshya Maheshwari in Swaragini (Colors TV).

Sukirti Khandpal, famous for her roles as Dr Riddhima Gupta in Dill Mill Gayye (Star One) opposite Karan Singh Grover sits pretty on the list.
